entries.femaleVariant: Eh, got what was coming to him.
Lizzie, what in the--? Fuck. Now I get the rush.
V, I-I was angry, I-I pushed him! These fucking arms, these hands! Oh my God…
So, this is about the body, right? That's why you called?
Yes, I... The media can't hear about this. Got it? That would be... Oohh...
Lizzy, snap the fuck out of it. What about the body?
OK. I'll take care of it.
No. Not doing it.
OK. I'll take care of it. You sleep soundly, now.
Sleep? I won't sleep. I don't need to.
Thank you, Liam. You don't realize it, but... you've given me something beautiful.
Shit... Guy's in shreds...
The world would eat it up. A tale of the temptation to control another's memory. A grim reminder that a "person" is merely a collection of bytes that can be copied, reproduced, copied, reproduced...
These wounds... You strangled him.
You strangled him, Lizzy. Slowly. You crushed his spine.
I... I was angry... I must've lost control.
Someone... Someone should give you a checkup, see if you're OK, Lizzy. Someone you trust.
The hell are you talkin' about?
Go, V. Go. And take him with you.
I like what's happening to me.
You've played your part in this story. Go.
I have nothing more to say to you.
No, not doin' it. Something... Somethin's not right, Lizzy.
entries.maleVariant: No, not doin' it. Somethin's... Somethin's not right, Lizzy.

entries.femaleVariant: No, quite the contrary. Everything's finally falling into place.
You ever wake up in the middle of the night... and not know who you were for a second…? Or, I mean... you ever feel like you weren't really "you?"
I... That's how I feel all the time. Every moment. This emptiness, this helplessness... I stopped seeing, creating... Just now, I--
What's done is done.
Liam was afraid of this...
Guy got what he deserved.
Welp, what's done is done.
So Liam really did have a reason to be afraid of you...
I didn't mean to, understand?! I didn't mean to!!
Sure, maybe. All the same to him, though.
entries.maleVariant: Sure, maybe. It's all the same to him, though.

entries.femaleVariant: Huh?
I dunno, do whatever. Take it somewhere, burn it. I'll pay you.
Go, V. And shut the door.
Lovely to meet you, V. Now go, go.
I just wanted to break up with him, you know? Tell him I wanted him out of my life... But I... I don't even know how, when I--
What about the body?
